{"tid":284740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果話威廉·渣甸靠鴉片起家, 會唔會比怡和告誹謗？","createTime":"2017-06-15T07:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T18:25:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"605b215c095bf6aeb17a69b4977abb953027647b","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"威廉&middot;渣甸，又譯「查頓」（Dr. William Jardine，1784年－1843年），蘇格蘭人，早年曾是一名在中國從事鴉片貿易的船上的外科醫生，後來創辦了怡和洋行，成為一名強大的商人，並在推動鴉片戰爭中起關鍵作用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg/300px-William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F48%2FWilliam_Jardine_in_Study.jpg%2F300px-William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg&h=7063765b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又真係未聽過, 怡和會告中學教科書出版社誹謗<br />\n<br />\n仲要係針一個已死既人, 普通法係唔可以提出誹謗<br />\n係要針對在生既人先得<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果</span></strong>怡和出律師信比我, 我一撚定去律師會投訴怡和律師違反專業守則<br />\n亂鳩出律師信<br />\n<br />\n睇下我上庭先, 定係個律師去紀律聆訊先"},{"pid":"e4c294bbe909e5b307727b81ef3715a0c3fbf348","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"怡和可能要考慮搵「墳場新聞」召返威廉&middot;渣甸上黎比口供先得"},{"pid":"b62b1ece9a5d076e835d69c66213c16728a7914f","tid":284740,"uid":4942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"利氏家族都係賣鴉片起家"},{"pid":"20271bac9bbcca5f5f122cd8f352761c09e5609a","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"其實全香港都靠鴉片起家<br />\n<br />\n唔係1842年英清戰爭, 我地邊有咁發呀？<br />\n<br />\n梁振英會唔會代表香港政府告我誹謗？<br />\n<br />\n我都未撚驚過啦！"},{"pid":"5ad9c6b8106d74c84a0e1d455e44f660b7958f35","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a69b286e73c21ce7480a3d6480446b7bc495a8","tid":284740,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"人地賣過百份 係唔同D"},{"pid":"029e018b9dd235bed6fdda0ab61e047f9f6b1741","tid":284740,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"有年書展有個talk,個講者話當年有人做過怡和定邊間老牌英資公司research, 應該份野寫到當年鴉片相關啲野, 份research要用到公司archive要俾間公司scan過, 個作者無留底, 成份做完俾間公司沒收左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e5ff897d281abff5b09925234f511adeb47386","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有年書展有個talk,個講者話當年有人做過怡和定邊間老牌英資公司research, 應該份野寫到當年鴉片相關啲野, 份research要用到公司archive要俾間公司scan過, 個作者無留底, 成份做完俾間公司沒收左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔係誹謗"},{"pid":"7ce194928265255e2e977f66c4f542248a2e5a78","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75ddc49d51116b97320f58f9b63f5d30cca13d4a","tid":284740,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>威廉&middot;渣甸，又譯「查頓」（Dr. William Jardine，1784年－1843年），蘇格蘭人，早年曾是一名在中國從事鴉片貿易的船上的外科醫生，後來創辦了怡和洋行，成為一名強大的商人，並在推動鴉片戰爭中起關鍵作用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg/300px-William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F48%2FWilliam_Jardine_in_Study.jpg%2F300px-William_Jardine_in_Study.jpg&h=7063765b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又真係未聽過, 怡和會告中學教科書出版社誹謗<br />\n<br />\n仲要係針一個已死既人, 普通法係唔可以提出誹謗<br />\n係要針對在生既人先得<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果</span></strong>怡和出律師信比我, 我一撚定去律師會投訴怡和律師違反專業守則<br />\n亂鳩出律師信<br />\n<br />\n睇下我上庭先, 定係個律師去紀律聆訊先</blockquote><br />\n因為嗰時冇犯法，冇人話自己係比人砌生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed763993810aef8c3c0a0d902776b4a308bfcbdc","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8619134bfb5a67a7354fbca3d635b0365d68a8f6","tid":284740,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efae79b02e4115caa7531a536ef7075c11878a5","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"751f1f3d1d1140d704dffc4462ba0855bf3b8a6a","tid":284740,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"英國佬不嬲話係藥用，任何人點食唔關賣果個事。"},{"pid":"8ff1a7069d8f9b3b3f905c3cc87a94dee59dcf96","tid":284740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國佬不嬲話係藥用，任何人點食唔關賣果個事。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都可以咁講<br />\n<br />\n不過英國佬當時比林則徐銷左超過700噸<br />\n<br />\n威廉&middot;渣甸都算係藥品大亨啦"},{"pid":"aed64cf76480d4eaa1e0132375f33cf048feae45","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ddf3c421f856af2bb384eba20c946223ece9afb","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59d28a5742f4d196a2fcde98b38c97f7f0c50dd8","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb911276995245214db671c0c544f23ba82c34c","tid":284740,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e345d6d6ed820fca08319979b58d6fc30e96e3e2","tid":284740,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime